{"tid":509232,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"Merry Christmas 🎅 我創作左一隻聖誕 Beat 想祝福大家，希望你會鍾意。","createTime":"2017-12-25T05:49:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T10:41:09.000Z","uid":164192,"like":221,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"86108722cfda2fb4f48867e9b02e24a83b7995d2","tid":509232,"uid":164192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:49:00.000Z","msg":"Merry Christmas,<br />\n送上一首聖誕 Beat，係輕快流行風格，<br />\n希望大家有一個美好幸福嘅聖誕。<br />\n願音樂可以洗滌遺憾、憂傷嘅心靈，<br />\n願音樂可以令幸福、快樂更加感到滿足。<br />\n🙏 Love &amp; Peace <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/P4Php7vsX0c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FP4Php7vsX0c&d=tChkqxY43xZa1fhjETCzmjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=8a5cfc26\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/P4Php7vsX0c</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後我會繼續創作多d 唔同類型、風格嘅伴奏，希望大家可以感受到唔同嘅氛圍同埋主題。<br />\nEnjoy the power of music, 多謝🙏 Peace<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你鍾意 hip hop music, 香港仲有好多人默默做依類型音樂，當中有好多唔同風格同技術，你可以去依度聽聽，相信你可以搵到更多 hip hop 嘅動人之處，實有一種你會鍾意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hk852rap/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhk852rap%2F&d=tChkqxY43xZa1fhjETCzmjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=1f7fc621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hk852rap/</a>"},{"pid":"e378bf9c497d25ce8b457e18f7bbe959a25fa026","tid":509232,"uid":132544,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:54:42.000Z","msg":"十卜"},{"pid":"570ee93a6f5bbc3dac32e374aba406b6f33cb947","tid":509232,"uid":132544,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05:59:41.000Z","msg":"個段rap做得幾好，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e6de4bf5dd4ab3886a85d437115c5ecadb6bf6","tid":509232,"uid":164192,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"570ee93a6f5bbc3dac32e374aba406b6f33cb947","tid":509232,"uid":132544,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T05: